rty%20(AAP)%20slammed%20the%20BJP%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20ruling%20party%20was%20panicking%20as%20it%20could%20sense%20defeat%2C%20Abhay%20Chautala's%20INLD%20too%20sought%20the%20deferment%20of%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Haryana%20BJP%20leader%20on%20Saturday%20said%20the%20letter%20was%20sent%20by%20the%20party's%20state%20unit%20chief%20Mohan%20Lal%20Badoli%20to%20the%20poll%20panel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana's%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer%20Pankaj%20Agarwal%20confirmed%20that%20the%20commission%20received%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20communication%20on%20Friday%20over%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20received%20the%20communication%20from%20state%20BJP%20and%20forwarded%20it%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%26quot%3B%20Agarwal%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVarinder%20Garg%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20BJP's%20state%20election%20management%20committee%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20reasoned%20that%20the%20Assembly%20election%20date%20of%20October%201%20(Tuesday)%20is%20preceded%20by%20a%20weekend%20and%20followed%20by%20more%20holidays%20which%20might%20hit%20the%20voting%20percentage%20as%20people%20tend%20to%20go%20on%20vacation%20on%20long%20weekends.%26quot%3B%20Varinder%20Garg%20said%20September%2028-29%20are%20Saturday%20and%20Sunday%20while%20October%201%20is%20a%20poll%20holiday.%20It%20is%20followed%20by%20more%20holidays%20as%20Gandhi%20Jayanti%20falls%20on%20October%202%20and%20Maharaja%20Agrasen%20Jayanti%20on%20October%203%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20written%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20in%20this%20regard.%20For%20a%20better%20turnout%2C%20any%20new%20date%20once%20the%20string%20of%20holidays%20is%20over%20should%20be%20fine%2C%26quot%3B%20Varinder%20Garg%20told%20PTI%20over%20the%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20taking%20a%20day's%20leave%20on%20September%2030%2C%20people%20will%20have%20six%20holidays.%20Due%20to%20this%20long%20weekend%2C%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20possibility%20that%20several%20families%20might%20go%20on%20a%20vacation%20and%20give%20voting%20a%20miss%2C%20Mohan%20Lal%20Badoli%20said%20in%20his%20letter%20to%20the%20EC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20it%20happens%2C%20the%20voting%20percentage%20would%20reduce%20drastically%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohan%20Lal%20Badoli%20also%20said%20that%20on%20'Asoj%20Amavasya'%20on%20October%202%2C%20several%20members%20of%20the%20Bishnoi%20community%20of%20Haryana%20will%20leave%20for%20Nokha%20tehsil%20of%20Bikaner%20in%20Rajasthan%20to%20participate%20in%20an%20annual%20fair%20held%20on%20the%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20too%20can%20affect%20the%20voting%20percentage%2C%20he%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohan%20Lal%20Badoli%20wrote%20that%20it%20has%20been%20the%20continuous%20effort%20of%20the%20EC%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20people%20exercise%20their%20franchise%20to%20strengthen%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20would%20be%20appropriate%20that%20the%20date%20fixed%20for%20voting%20for%20the%20Haryana%20Assembly%20election%20be%20changed.%20While%20determining%20a%20fresh%20date%20for%20the%20election%2C%20it%20should%20be%20made%20certain%20that%20there%20is%20no%20holiday%20the%20previous%20or%20the%20following%20day%2C%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20believe%20that%20if%20the%20EC%20does%20this%2C%20more%20and%20more%20voters%20will%20be%20able%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20election%2C%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohan%20Lal%20Badoli%2C%20in%20his%20letter%2C%20also%20mentioned%20that%20in%20the%20past%20the%20date%20of%20polling%20has%20been%20changed%20by%20the%20EC.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20date%20declared%20for%20voting%20in%20Punjab%20Assembly%20elections%20--%20February%2014%2C%202022%20--%20was%20changed%20to%20February%2020%2C%202022%2C%20due%20to%20Sant%20Ravidas%20Jayanti%20on%20February%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20then%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Charanjit%20Singh%20Channi%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%2C%20and%20the%20BSP%20had%20urged%20the%20poll%20panel%20to%20postpone%20the%20date%20of%20voting%20as%20lakhs%20of%20followers%20of%20Guru%20Ravidas%20travel%20to%20Varanasi%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20celebrate%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Hooda%20said%20the%20BJP's%20stand%20shows%20that%20it%20has%20already%20accepted%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20more%20than%20a%20week%20since%20the%20Election%20Commission%20announced%20the%20poll%20date.%20The%20BJP%20wants%20the%20polls%20to%20be%20deferred%20as%20it%20has%20accepted%20defeat%2C%20Bhupinder%20Hooda%2C%20who%20is%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20Haryana%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolls%20should%20be%20held%20according%20to%20the%20date%20fixed%20by%20the%20EC...%20People%20of%20Haryana%20don't%20want%20to%20see%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20power%20even%20for%20a%20day%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhupinder%20Hooda's%20son%20and%20Rohtak%20MP%20Deepender%20Hooda%20while%20referring%20to%20Mohan%20Lal%20Badoli's%20letter%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20shows%20how%20scared%20the%20BJP%20is%20of%20the%20elections%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20staring%20at%20defeat%20and%20is%20therefore%20coming%20up%20with%20such%20childish%20arguments.%20It%20has%20no%20issues%2C%20work%20or%20achievements%20to%20show%20to%20the%20people%20and%20no%20candidates%20to%20distribute%20the%20tickets.%20This%20is%20why%20the%20BJP%20is%20conspiring%20to%20postpone%20the%20elections%20by%20giving%20an%20excuse%20for%20holidays%2C%20Deepender%20Hooda%20said%20in%20Hindi%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20voters%20of%20Haryana%20are%20aware.%20They%20will%20not%20go%20anywhere%20for%20a%20holiday%2C%20but%20will%20come%20to%20the%20polling%20booth%20in%20large%20numbers%20to%20vote%20out%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP's%20Haryana%20unit%20said%20even%20before%20the%20elections%20took%20place%2C%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20had%20started%20looking%20for%20excuses%20as%20it%20could%20sense%20its%20impending%20defeat%20in%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20the%20AAP%20said%20if%20the%20BJP%20had%20done%20work%20in%20the%20state%2C%20it%20would%20not%20have%20been%20seeking%20postponement%20of%20polls.%20This%20time%20the%20BJP's%20defeat%20is%20certain%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal's%20(INLD)%20Chautala%20said%20the%20polling%20date%20should%20be%20postponed%20by%20one%20or%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20people%20usually%20go%20on%20holidays%20on%20long%20weekends%2C%20it%20will%20adversely%20affect%20the%20voting%20percentage%20which%20is%20likely%20to%20decrease%20by%2015%20to%2020%20per%20cent%2C%20Chautala%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EC%20on%20August%2016%20announced%20that%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Haryana%20would%20be%20held%20in%20a%20single%20phase%20on%20October%201%20and%20the%20results%20would%20be%20declared%20on%20October%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20eyeing%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%20while%20the%20Congress%20is%20looking%20to%20wrest%20power%20from%20the%20ruling%20outfit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tenure%20of%20the%20current%20Haryana%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20ends%20on%20November%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724524500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F457qkoc_nayab-saini_625x300_25_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-targets-bjp-after-it-requests-poll-body-to-postpone-voting-day-6410958%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Haryana%20unit%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20