owd%20had%20gathered%20at%20the%20spot%2C%20the%20cops%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20case%20under%20relevant%20sections%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyay%20Sanhita%20and%20the%20Informational%20Technology%20Act%2C%20has%20been%20registered%20and%20investigations%20are%20on%20to%20arrest%20the%20people%20involved%20in%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20cops%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDMC%20said%20it%20could%20be%20a%20case%20of%20%26quot%3Bhacking%26quot%3B%20the%20screen%20by%20using%20advanced%20technology.%20The%20civic%20body%20said%20it%20operates%20two%20types%20of%20panels%20in%20the%20areas%20under%20its%20jurisdiction--%20one%20for%20advertisement%20and%20another%20for%20an%20interactive%20touchscreen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20panels%20are%20of%20international%20standard%20and%20controlled%20by%20a%20server%20which%20is%20completely%20secured%20with%20a%20firewall%20and%20antivirus.%20We%20are%20also%20providing%20hotspots%20free%20of%20cost%20for%20public%20usage%20in%20the%20NDMC%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConnaught%20Place%20is%20an%20iconic%20and%20historic%20commercial%20area%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20national%20capital.%20Thousands%20of%20people%20visit%20the%20market%20daily%20and%20footfall%20increases%20on%20weekends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20a%20glitch%20like%20this%20has%20been%20reported.%20A%20similar%20incident%20occurred%20last%20year%20in%20Bihar%2C%20where%20a%20porn%20clip%20was%20played%20at%20Patna%20railway%20station%20on%20the%20display%20screen%20meant%20for%20advertisements.%20The%20Railway%20Protection%20Force%20stepped%20in%20and%20stopped%20the%20footage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20With%20inputs%20from%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724516640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-03%2F4dbblj4s_connaught-place-generic-istock_625x300_20_March_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fporn-video-runs-on-ad-board-at-delhis-connaught-place-case-filed-6410307%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20porn%20video%20was%20played%20on%20a%20digital%20advertisement%20board%20in%20Delhi's%20Connaught%20Place%2C%20one%20of%20the%20busiest%20markets%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fporn-video-runs-on-ad-board-at-delhis-connaught-place-case-filed-6410307%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NASA%20announces%20decision%20on%20plan%20to%20return%20stranded%20astronauts%20to%20Earth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724516400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F08%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-astronauts-butch-wilmore_6650647.jpg%3F20240808094848%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fastronauts-stranded-on-space-station-to-return-next-february-nasa-announces-13202563%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22NASA%20has%20announced%20the%20two%20astronauts%20stranded%20on%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20(ISS)%20will%20return%20to%20Earth%20on%20SpaceX%20in%20February%202025.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1662%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fastronauts-stranded-on-space-station-to-return-next-february-nasa-announces-13202563%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fastronauts-stranded-on-space-station-to-return-next-february-nasa-announces-13202563%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fastronauts-stranded-on-space-station-to-return-next-february-nasa-announces-13202563%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWill%20Benefit%2023%20Lakh%20Employees%26quot%3B%3A%20Centre%20Launches%20Unified%20Pension%20Scheme%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20big%20announcement%20ahead%20of%20assembly%20elections%20in%20one%20state%20and%20a%20Union%20Territory%20this%20year%2C%20the%20government%20has%20launched%20the%20Unified%20Pension%20Scheme%20(UPS)%20amid%20protests%20by%20several%20non-BJP-ruled%20states%20over%20the%20New%20Pension%20Scheme%20(NPS).%20%26quot%3BThis%20scheme%20will%20benefit%2023%20lakh%20central%20government%20employees%20(under%20the%20National%20Pension%20Scheme)%2C%26quot%3B%20announced%20Union%20Information%20and%20Broadcasting%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw.%20The%20new%20scheme%20will%20be%20implemented%20from%20April%201%2C%202025%20and%20employees%20will%20have%20the%20option%20to%20choose%20between%20the%20NPS%20or%20UPS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UPS%2C%20approved%20by%20the%20Union%20Cabinet%20chaired%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20aims%20to%20give%20assured%20pension%2C%20family%20pension%20and%20assured%20minimum%20pension%20to%20government%20employees%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Assured%20Pension%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20scheme%20assures%2050%20percent%20of%20the%20average%20basic%20salary%20for%20the%20last%2012%20months%20before%20retirement%20as%20the%20pension%20for%20government%20employees%20who%20complete%20a%20minimum%20of%2025%20years%20in%20service.%20It%20will%20be%20proportionate%20for%20a%20shorter%20service%20period%20up%20to%20a%20minimum%20of%2010%20years%20of%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Assured%20Family%20Pension%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20case%20of%20death%2C%20the%20family%20will%20get%2060%20percent%20of%20the%20last-drawn%20amount%20by%20the%20pensioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Assured%20Minimum%20Pension%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20scheme%20also%20assures%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20month%20after%20retirement%20for%20government%20employees%20after%20minimum%2010%20years%20of%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20current%20pension%20scheme%2C%20employees%20contribute%2010%20per%20cent%20while%20the%20central%20government%20contributes%2014%20percent%2C%20which%20would%20be%20increased%20to%2018.5%20percent%20with%20the%20UPS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20central%20employees%20met%20with%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20today.%20They%20were%20with%20the%20UPS%20in%20the%20meeting%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Vaishnaw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20the%20centre%20is%20%26quot%3Bproud%20of%20the%20hard%20work%20of%20all%20government%20employees%20who%20contribute%20significantly%20to%20national%20progress%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Unified%20Pension%20Scheme%20ensures%20dignity%20and%20financial%20security%20for%20government%20employees%2C%20aligning%20with%20our%20commitment%20to%20their%20well-being%20and%20a%20secure%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20a%20committee%20under%20Finance%20Secretary%20TV%20Somanathan%20was%20set%20up%20to%20review%20the%20pension%20scheme%20for%20government%20employees%20and%20suggest%20changes%20in%20the%20light%20of%20the%20existing%20framework%20and%20structure%20of%20the%20National%20Pension%20System.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20finance%20ministry%20formed%20the%20committee%20after%20several%20non-BJP-ruled%20states%20decided%20to%20revert%20to%20the%20Old%20Pension%20Scheme%20(OPS)%20and%20calls%20by%20employee%20organisations%20for%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20OPS%2C%20retired%20government%20employees%20received%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20their%20last-drawn%20salary%20as%20monthly%20pensions.%20The%20amount%20keeps%20increasing%20with%20the%20hike%20in%20the%20Dearness%20Allowance%20(DA)%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724515680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fs3usg04_pm-pension-_625x300_24_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funion-cabinet-approves-unified-pension-scheme-says-will-benefit-23-lakh-central-employees-6409535%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20big%20announcement%20ahead%20of%20assembly%20elections%20in%20one%20state%20and%