he%2059th%20Raising%20Day%20of%20Border%20Security%20Force%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20incidents%20of%20Maoist%20violence%20have%20gone%20down%20by%2052%20per%20cent%2C%20deaths%20in%20these%20incidents%20declined%20by%2070%20per%20cent%20and%20the%20number%20of%20affected%20districts%20have%20come%20down%20from%2096%20to%2045.%26quot%3B%20The%20number%20of%20%26quot%3BLWE-hit%20police%20stations%20has%20come%20down%20from%20495%20to%20176%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20press%20briefing%20today%2C%20the%20Home%20Minister%20reiterated%20the%20facts%20and%20said%2C%20there%20was%20a%2053%20per%20cent%20drop%20in%20Naxal%20incidents%20during%202014-24%20as%20compared%20to%202004-14.%20It%20is%20time%20to%20deal%20the%20final%20blow%20to%20the%20problem%20of%20Left%20Wing%20Extremism%20with%20a%20strong%20strategy.%C2%A0%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20free%20the%20country%20from%20Left%20Wing%20Extremism%20by%20March%202026%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20added%20that%20the%20government%20has%20been%20working%20to%20fill%20the%20security%20vacuum%20in%20LWE-hit%20areas%20and%20the%20security%20personnel%20have%20undertaken%20operations%20along%20with%20development%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20said%20apart%20from%20state%20and%20Central%20Armed%20Police%20Forces%2C%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%2C%20the%20country's%20premier%20anti-terror%20probe%20agency%20and%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20have%20been%20working%20together%20to%20wipe%20out%20Maoist%20extremism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Home%20Ministry's%20Left%20Wing%20Extremism%20(LWE)%20Division%2C%20which%20was%20established%20in%202006%2C%20addresses%20the%20issue%20holistically.%20It%20monitors%20the%20LWE%20situation%20and%20countermeasures%20being%20taken%20by%20the%20affected%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Division%20is%20responsible%20for%20capacity%20building%20of%20states%20to%20combat%20LWE%20through%20schemes%20of%20the%20Home%20Ministry%20like%20the%20Security%20Related%20Expenditure%20(SRE)%20scheme%2C%20Special%20Infrastructure%20Scheme%2C%20and%20Special%20Central%20Assistance.%20Deployment%20of%20Central%20Armed%20Police%20Forces%20(CAPFs)%20in%20the%20affected%20States%2C%20assisting%20State%20Governments%20with%20initiatives%20to%20combat%20extremism%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20With%20Inputs%20from%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724512140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F6o7bsh4_amit-shah_625x300_19_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fend-of-the-line-for-maoism-by-march-2026-amit-shah-sets-big-target-6409799%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20has%20set%202026%20as%20the%20target%20to%20finish%20Maoist%20activities%20in%20India%20and%20said%20%26quot%3BA%20strong%20and%20ruthless%20strategy%20is%20required%20for%20launching%20the%20last%20assault%20against%20such%20groups.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fend-of-the-line-for-maoism-by-march-2026-amit-shah-sets-big-target-6409799%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Govt%20approves%20Unified%20Pension%20Scheme%2C%20to%20benefit%202.3%20mn%20central%20employees%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724511909000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-02%2F29%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1709207731-796.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fgovt-approves-unified-pension-scheme-to-benefit-2-3-mn-central-employees-124082400773_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20will%20be%20an%20option%20for%20the%20employees%20to%20opt%20between%20NPS%20and%20UPS%2C%20said%20Union%20Mini