s%20wake.%20Despite%20the%20suspension%20of%20eight%20officials%2C%20two%20of%20whom%20have%20since%20retired%20and%20the%20others%20reinstated%2C%20and%20the%20blacklisting%20of%20the%20construction%20company%2C%20no%20accountability%20has%20been%20established%20for%20the%20massive%20failure%20that%20endangered%20over%2018%20villages%20and%20devastated%20the%20livelihoods%20of%20farmers%20in%2042%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2011%2C%202022%2C%20the%20first%20signs%20of%20trouble%20were%20detected%20with%20a%20leak%20in%20the%20Karam%20Dam.%20The%20government%20and%20local%20administration%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20breach%20the%20incomplete%20wall%20to%20prevent%20a%20larger%20catastrophe.%20For%20three%20nights%2C%20they%20worked%20tirelessly%20to%20release%20the%20water%20safely.%20Yet%2C%20after%20the%20initial%20crisis%20was%20averted%2C%20attention%20waned%2C%20leaving%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnear-catastrophe-at-madhya-pradeshs-karam-dam-brings-scam-shadow-in-focus-again-3262804%5C%22%3EKaram%20Dam%3C%2Fa%3E%20abandoned%20and%20the%20affected%20villagers%20in%20a%20state%20of%20despair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFertile%20Lands%20Destroyed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dam%20was%20originally%20intended%20to%20irrigate%20the%20agricultural%20lands%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshivraj-chouhan-warns-villagers-as-damaged-dam-in-dhar-is-emptied-3254721%5C%22%3E42%20villages%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Dharampuri%20tehsil.%20However%2C%20since%20the%20breach%2C%20the%20flood-affected%20tribal%20farmers%20have%20been%20struggling%20to%20survive.%20Their%20fertile%20lands%20were%20destroyed%2C%20replaced%20by%20fields%20filled%20with%20stones%20from%20the%20floodwaters.%20The%20result%20is%20that%20many%20farmers%2C%20like%20Shivam%20Kahir%2C%20have%20been%20forced%20into%20labor%20work%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDue%20to%20the%20Karam%20Dam%20bursting%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20our%20land%20and%20crops%20were%20destroyed.%20The%20fertile%20soil%20was%20washed%20away%2C%20and%20now%20our%20fields%20are%20filled%20with%20stones.%20We%20have%20resupeatedly%20asked%20the%20government%20for%20compensation%20and%20to%20restore%20our%20land%2C%20but%20nothing%20has%20been%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Shivam%2C%20expressing%20the%20frustration%20felt%20by%20many%20in%20his%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20so%20dire%20that%20some%20villagers%20have%20taken%20refuge%20in%20the%20nearby%20forests%2C%20leaving%20their%20homes%20behind.%20They%20face%20daily%20hardships%2C%20including%20a%20lack%20of%20food%20and%20basic%20necessities.%20Many%20villagers%2C%20like%20Jaisingh%2C%20have%20issued%20a%20stern%20warning%20to%20the%20government%3A%20if%20problems%20are%20not%20addressed%2C%20they%20will%20obstruct%20any%20further%20work%20on%20the%20dam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20agency%20responsible%20for%20the%20dam's%20construction%20made%20us%20sign%20consent%20forms%2C%20but%20now%20they've%20been%20given%20the%20contract%20again.%20If%20they%20don't%20remove%20the%20debris%20from%20our%20fields%20before%20resuming%20work%2C%20we%20will%20not%20allow%20them%20to%20start%2C%26quot%3B%20Jaisingh%20warns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'No%20Electricity%2C%20Roads%20For%202%20Years'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20are%20also%20demanding%20compensation%20akin%20to%20what%20was%20provided%20to%20those%20affected%20by%20the%20Narmada%20floods.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20without%20electricity%2C%20water%2C%20and%20roads%20for%20two%20years.%20We%20should%20be%20compensated%20just%20like%20the%20Narmada%20flood-affected%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Kamal%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Utavali%20village.%20He%20highlights%20the%20severe%20neglect%20from%20the%20government%2C%20stating%20that%20despite%20the%20compensation%20for%20land%2C%20no%20reparations%20have%20been%20made%20for%20the%20loss%20of%20trees%2C%20wells%2C%20or%20other%20essential%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiving%20conditions%20for%20the%20displaced%20farmers%20are%20deplorable.%20They%20reside%20in%20makeshift%20shelters%20in%20the%20forests%2C%20facing%20threats%20from%20wild%20animals%20and%20lacking%20basic%20amenities%20such%20as%20electricity%20and%20roads.%20Education%20for%20children%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20makeshift%20classes%20held%20in%20huts%2C%20and%20the%20community%20remains%20in%20a%20constant%20state%20of%20fear%20and%20insecurity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20affected%20tribal%20farmers%20were%20given%20Rs%202%20lakh%20per%20bigha%20as%20compensation%2C%20which%20was%20insufficient.%20They%20were%20promised%20homes%20and%20land%20in%20return%2C%20but%20two%20years%20later%2C%20they%20are%20still%20waiting%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Panchilal%20Meda%2C%20a%20former%20MLA%20from%20Congress.%20He%20further%20accuses%20the%20government%20of%20gross%20corruption%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20dam%2C%20which%20cost%20Rs%20305%20crore%2C%20was%20built%20using%20substandard%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20allegations%2C%20government%20officials%20maintain%20that%20most%20of%20the%20compensation%20has%20been%20distributed.%20%26quot%3BOnly%20a%20few%20people%20are%20left%20to%20receive%20compensation.%20We%20are%20working%20on%20completing%20this%20process%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20investigate%20and%20compensate%20those%20eligible%2C%26quot%3B%20states%20MS%20Chauhan%2C%20executive%20engineer.%20He%20adds%20that%20due%20to%20the%20complexity%20of%20the%20project%2C%20the%20construction%20work%20will%20take%20another%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20ANS%20Construction%20from%20Delhi%20was%20awarded%20the%20contract%20to%20build%20the%20Karam%20Dam.%20ANS%20subcontracted%20the%20work%20to%20Gwalior's%20Sarathi%20Construction.%20Following%20the%20dam's%20failure%2C%20both%20companies%20were%20blacklisted