%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrice%20gouging%20skepticism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20has%20elicited%20a%20range%20of%20responses%20from%20experts%20and%20economists%2C%20with%20some%20deriding%20it%20as%20an%20unnecessary%20overstep%20by%20the%20government%20to%20address%20a%20problem%20that%20is%20not%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20inflation%20dilemma.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hope%20she%20walks%20this%20one%20back.%20She%20had%20some%20good%20ideas%2C%20some%20mixed%20ideas%2C%26quot%3B%20Harvard%20professor%20Kenneth%20Rogoff%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F08%2F17%2Fpolitics%2Fvideo%2Fharris-economic-vision-professor-rogoff-digvid%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20a%20horrible%20idea.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERogoff's%20position%20was%20based%20on%20doubts%20about%20whether%20retailers%20were%20to%20blame%20for%20the%20wave%20of%20inflation%20that%20has%20weighed%20on%20Americans'%20spending%20power%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHarris%20called%20for%20a%20first-ever%20federal%20ban%20on%20the%20basis%20that%20firms%20have%20notched%20record%20profits%20at%20a%20time%20when%20many%20households%20have%20struggled%20to%20adjust%20to%20runaway%20costs.%20Since%20January%202020%2C%20grocery%20prices%20have%20jumped%2025%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20according%20to%20market%20veteran%20Ed%20Yardeni%2C%20data%20doesn't%20suggest%20gouging%20is%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20wrote%20this%20week%20that%20the%20ratio%20between%20the%20consumer%20price%20index%20and%20supermarket%20producer%20price%20index%20has%20been%20dropping%20since%202000%2C%20suggesting%20that%20profit%20margins%20in%20the%20industry%20have%20been%20trending%20down%2C%20not%20up.%20CPI%20tracks%20prices%20paid%20by%20consumers%2C%20while%20PPI%20measures%20the%20prices%20paid%20by%20wholesalers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20consumers%20feel%20strongly%20that%20corporate%20greed%20is%20a%20central%20factor%20for%20why%20prices%20have%20risen%20abruptly.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsocialeconomicslab.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhy_dislike_inflation.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20May%2C%20price%20gouging%20was%20the%20second%20leading%20perceived%20cause%20of%20inflation%20among%20surveyed%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReal-world%20examples%20do%20exist.%20Cal-Maine%2C%20the%20largest%20egg%20producer%20in%20the%20US%2C%20saw%20its%20profits%20rocket%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2023%2F03%2F29%2Fbusiness%2Fegg-profits-cal-maine%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E718%25%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202023%3C%2Fa%3E.%20By%20December%2C%20the%20distributor%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Flegal%2Flitigation%2Fus-jury-awards-177-mln-kraft-other-producers-egg-price-fixing-case-2023-12-01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%20liable%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20artificially%20inflating%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Price%20controls'%20a%20partisan%20label%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20gouging%20deserves%20the%20blame%20for%20inflation%2C%20some%20have%20also%20criticized%20Harris'%20plan%20as%20an%20ineffective%20government%20overreach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPundits%20have%20alluded%20to%20the%20price%20controls%20under%20President%20Richard%20Nixon.%20The%20Republican%20executive%20froze%20prices%20and%20wages%20over%20fifty%20years%20ago%20to%20clamp%20down%20on%20inflation%2C%20but%20it%20eventually%20jumped%20much%20higher%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cato.org%2Fblog%2Funhappy-40th-anniversary-nixons-wage-price-controls%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECato%20Institute%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20libertarian%20think%20tank.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20all%20of%20us%20would%20agree%20that%20price%20controls%20have%20never%20worked%2C%26quot%3B%20Stephen%20Moore%2C%20visiting%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20conservative%20think%20tank%20Heritage%20Foundation%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2Fvideo%2F2024%2F08%2F19%2Fharris-price-gouging-proposal-is-a-common-sense-set-of-policies-groundworkas-lindsay-owens.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNBC%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThey%20certainly%20were%20a%20complete%20failure%20in%20the%201970s%20when%20we%20had%20major%20inflation%20that%20hit%2011%25-12%25%20and%20the%20government%20couldn't%20get%20rid%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBroader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stlouisfed.org%2Fpublications%2Fregional-economist%2F2022%2Fmar%2Fwhy-price-controls-should-stay-history-books%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexamples%20through%20history%3C%2Fa%3E%20show%20that%20price%20ceilings%20can%20distort%20the%20allocation%20of%20goods%20and%20supply%2C%20as%20prices%20no%20longer%20serve%20to%20signal%20a%20surplus%20or%20scarcity.%20This%20can%20eventually%20lead%20to%20shortages%20and%20higher%20pricing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20supporters%20of%20the%20plan%20argue%20that%20such%20comparisons%20are%20an%20overreaction%20to%20Harris's%20proposal%2C%20as%20the%20details%20thus%20far%20say%20nothing%20about%20fixing%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20'price%20controls.'%2040%20states%20have%20price%20gouging%20laws%20on%20the%20books.%20These%20are%20red%20states.%20These%20are%20blue%20states%2C%26quot%3B%20Groundwork%20Collaborative%20executive%20director%20Lindsay%20Owens%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20Donald%20Trump%20also%20cracked%20down%20medical%20supply%20price%20gouging%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20common-sense%20set%20of%20policies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20ban%20would%20help%20patch%20up%20legal%20inconsistencies%20between%20each%20state's%20approach%2C%20experts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-lower-grocery-prices-inflation-harris-price-gouging-proposal-2024-8%3Fas%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Harris%20would%20likely%20find%20success%20by%20empowering%20the%20Federal%20Trade%20Commission%20to%20pursue%20bad%20actors%2C%20though%20the%20challenge%20would%20lie%20in%20carefully%20defining%20price%20gouging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20plan's%20advocates%20have%20cheered%20this%20on%2C%20anonymous%20campaign%20sources%20that%20spoke%20with%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20noted%20that%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F08%2F21%2Fbusiness%2Feconomy%2Fharris-price-gouging-ban-groceries.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eallies%20may%20have%20the%20wrong%20idea%20about%20what%20it%20can%20do%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20it%20would%20be%20modeled%20on%20state%20laws%2C%20the%20ban%20would%20really%20only%20come%20into%20effect%20in%20emergencies%2C%20officials%20said%2C%20stating%20that%20just%20as%20price-control%20critiques%20are%20misguided%2C%20so%20are%20expectations%20that%20the%20ban%20will%20immediately%20cut%20down%20on%20grocery%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20that%20to%20happen%2C%20a%20campaign%20official%20cited%20Harris'%20other%20policy%20ideas%2C%20such%20as%20efforts%20to%20spur%20competition%20and%20support%20small%20businesses%20in%20the%20food%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20economists%20are%20divided%2C%20voters%20seem%20supportive%20of%20the%20proposal.%20Summer%20polling%20from%20the%20Democratic%20firm%20Blueprint%20found%20that%20four%20out%20of%20five%20voters%20are%20in%20favor%20of%20price-gouging%20prosecution%2C%20as%20well%20as%20price%20fixing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkamala-harris-economic-plan-price-controls-gouging-food-inflation-election-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724502662000%2C%22visual%22%3A%