ure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lanette%20Canen%20and%20Bodin%20smiling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8bfd043b5e59d16b4bd66%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221725%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBodin%20told%20BI%20that%20before%20Villa%20Vie%2C%20the%20couple%20had%20never%20really%20considered%20leaving%20Maui.%3Cp%3ELanette%20Canen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20said%20they%20sold%20their%20car%20rental%20business%20in%20Maui%20%E2%80%94%20a%20fleet%20of%2031%20vehicles%20listed%20on%20Turo%20%E2%80%94%20to%20buy%20their%20%26quot%3Bobstructed%20view%26quot%3B%20cabin%20on%20Odyssey.%20(They%20declined%20to%20disclose%20the%20price%2C%20but%20windowless%20inside%20cabins%20are%20currently%20listed%20at%20%24100%2C000%2C%20while%20those%20with%20ocean%20views%20are%20%2450%2C000%20more.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20have%20to%20pay%20%243%2C500%20in%20monthly%20fees.%20But%20Canen%2C%20who%20plans%20to%20run%20her%20auto%20glass%20company%20remotely%20from%20the%20ship%2C%20said%20her%20income%20would%20cover%20this%20additional%20expense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20cabin%20is%20small%2C%20and%20a%20lifeboat%20obstructs%20its%20view%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20we're%20going%20to%20use%20it%20as%20our%20bedroom%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20ship%20as%20our%20living%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20Canen%20told%20BI.%20She%20said%20living%20in%20Maui%20is%20%26quot%3Bway%20more%20expensive%26quot%3B%20than%20the%20Odyssey.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20traveling%20on%20a%20budget.%20It's%20very%20affordable%20for%20the%20two%20of%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lifelong%20voyage%20was%20initially%20scheduled%20to%20set%20sail%20in%20May%20following%20Villa%20Vie's%20acquisition%20of%20Fred%20Olsen%20Cruise%20Lines'%20more%20than%2030-year-old%20Braemar%20vessel%2C%20now%20renamed%20Villa%20Vie%20Odyssey.%20However%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUDyF93CvpPA%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20issues%20like%20the%20aging%20ship's%20rudder%20stocks%20and%20recertification%20have%20delayed%20its%20departure%20by%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20other%20would-be%20Villa%20Vie%20cruisers%2C%20the%20couple%20left%20the%20US%20in%20May%20to%20make%20the%20ship's%20initial%20sail%20date.%20Since%20then%2C%20they've%20stayed%20in%20Europe%20in%20anticipation%20of%20its%20departure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResidents%20can%20spend%20their%20days%20on%20Odyssey%20but%20aren't%20allowed%20to%20stay%20overnight%20yet.%20Petterson%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20company%20is%20providing%20residents%20with%20shuttles%20to%20and%20from%20the%20ship%2C%20food%2C%20drinks%2C%20excursions%2C%20and%20lodging%20%E2%80%94%20or%20a%20daily%20per%20diem%20for%20those%20who%20%26quot%3Bchoose%20to%20do%20their%20own%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20went%20pretty%20much%20every%20day%20for%20two%20weeks%20and%20spent%20all%20day%20there%20until%20they%20kicked%20us%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20Canen%20told%20BI.%20She%20would%20go%20to%20the%20business%20center%20to%20work%20while%20Bodin%20would%20record%20videos%20for%20their%20YouTube%20channel%20and%20edit%20them%20in%20the%20observatory%20lounge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222300%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bodin%20holding%20a%20beer%20smiling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8bf8843b5e59d16b4bd31%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221150%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECanen%20and%20Bodin%20were%20able%20to%20explore%20the%20ship%20as%20they%20waited%20for%20its%20departure.%3Cp%3ELanette%20Canen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20say%20the%20food's%20been%20good%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20the%20barbecue%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they've%20had%20access%20to%20an%20open%20bar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20understand%20there%20are%20hiccups%2C%26quot%3B%20Bodin%20told%20BI.%20%2