m%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Findian-telecom-players-targetting-10-share-in-6g-patents-in-next-3-yrs-124082400581_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Findian-telecom-players-targetting-10-share-in-6g-patents-in-next-3-yrs-124082400581_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Findian-telecom-players-targetting-10-share-in-6g-patents-in-next-3-yrs-124082400581_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Encounter%20Breaks%20Out%20In%20J%26amp%3BK's%20Sopore%2C%20Searches%20On%2C%20Area%20Cordoned%20Off%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20encounter%20broke%20out%20between%20security%20forces%20and%20terrorists%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Sopore.%20The%20forces%20have%20cordoned%20off%20the%20Watergam%20area%20of%20Sopore%20and%20a%20search%20is%20on%2C%20the%20Kashmir%20Zone%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20details%20are%20awaited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20an%20encounter%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory's%20Udhampar%20region%20where%20a%20paramilitary%20officer%20from%20CRPF%20was%20killed%20in%20action%20after%20the%20terrorists%20fired%20upon%20a%20patrol%20party.%20Inspector%20Kuldeep%20Kumar%20from%20187%20Batallion%20of%20CRPF%20suffered%20gunshot%20wounds%20in%20the%20attack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERise%20In%20Terror%20Attacks%20In%20Jammu%20And%20Kashmir%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20spurt%20of%20terror%20activities%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20On%20August%2014%2C%20an%20army%20officer%2C%20Captain%20Deepak%20Singh%2C%20was%20killed%20in%20action%20after%20an%20encounter%20broke%20out%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Doda.%20A%20civilian%20was%20also%20injured%20in%20the%20incident.%20The%20officer%20suffered%20gunshot%20wounds%20in%20a%20forested%20area%20during%20a%20cordon-and-search%20operation%20in%20the%20Shivgarh-Assar%20belt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20chaired%20a%20high-level%20meeting%20over%20rising%20terror%20attacks%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20after%20back-to-back%20encounters%20and%20ambushes%20took%20place.%20The%20meeting%20was%20held%20at%20the%20South%20Block%20in%20Delhi%2C%20with%20NSA%20Ajit%20Doval%20and%20Army%20Chief%20General%20Upendra%20Dwivedi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2010%2C%20two%20soldiers%20and%20a%20civilian%20were%20killed%20during%20a%20gunfight%20between%20terrorists%20and%20security%20forces%20in%20Anantnag.%20The%20region%20has%20witnessed%20attacks%20on%20an%20army%20convoy%20in%20Kathua%2C%20skirmishes%20in%20Doda%20and%20Udhampur%2C%20and%20a%20failed%20attack%20by%20the%20Pakistan%20Border%20Action%20Team%20(BAT)%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20(LoC)%20in%20Kupwara%20district's%20Machchal%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%2C%2028%20people%2C%20including%20civilians%20and%20security%20personnel%2C%20were%20killed%20in%2011%20terror-related%20incidents%20and%2024%20counter-terror%20operations%20up%20to%20July%2021%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAction%20Plan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0The%20government%2C%20while%20maintaining%20a%20focus%20on%20securing%20the%20Kashmir%20Valley%2C%20has%20also%20recognised%20the%20need%20to%20bolster%20security%20in%20the%20Jammu%20region.%20This%20has%20resulted%20in%20the%20mobilisation%20of%20additional%20forces%20for%20deployment%20in%20key%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20primary%20objectives%20of%20the%20government's%20new%20security%20strategy%20is%20to%20plug%20infiltration%20routes%20used%20by%20terrorists%20to%20enter%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20audits%20conducted%20by%20various%20agencies%20identified%20about%20two%20dozen%20sectors%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%20(LOC)%20in%20the%20valley%20and%20the%20international%20border%20in%20the%20Jammu%20sector.%20Terrorists%20often%20take%20help%20from%20local%20guides%20to%20cross%20over.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20terrorists%20are%20equipped%20with%20sophisticated%20weapons%20like%20the%20American-made%20M4%20assault%20ride%20with%20an%20infrared%20thermal%20sight%20and%20are%20trained%20in%20jungle%20warfare.%20Terrorists%20infiltrate%20by%20foot%20and%20the%20government%20has%20initiated%20a%20project%20to%20fence%20the%20borders%20however%20the%20progress%20has%20been%20slow%20with%20only%2070%20kilometres%20being%20covered%20out%20of%20180%20kilometres.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724498940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-03%2Fsecurity-forces-kashmir-generic_650x400_51520188882.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fencounter-breaks-out-in-j-ks-sopore-searches-on-area-cordoned-off-6408498%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20encounter%20broke%20out%20between%20security%20forces%20and%20terrorists%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Sopore.%20The%20forces%20have%20cordoned%20off%20the%20Watergam%20area%20of%20Sopore%20and%20a%20search%20is%20on.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fencounter-breaks-out-in-j-ks-sopore-searches-on-area-cordoned-off-6408498%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Houthi%20rebels%20release%20footage%20of%20explosion%20on%20Red%20Sea%20tanker%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724497920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F08%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-houthi-rebels-sounion-tanker_6664923.jpg%3F20240824121522%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhouthi-rebels-release-footage-of-explosion-on-red-sea-tanker-13202131%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yemen's%20Houthi%20rebels%20have%20shared%20a%20video%20showing%20an%20explosion%20and%