%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAkash%20with%20his%20younger%20sister.%20On%20the%20right%20are%20his%20cousin%20and%20sister-in-law%20who%20took%20him%20in.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkash%E2%80%99s%20goals%20were%20never%20deterred%20by%20his%20cousin%E2%80%99s%20meagre%20resources.%20He%20encouraged%20him%20to%20strive%20high%20and%20follow%20his%20aspirations.%20He%20eventually%20pursued%20mechanical%20engineering%20from%20a%20local%20college%20in%20Vadodara%20where%20he%20was%20inspired%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20UPSC%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20naturally%20inclined%20to%20social%20work%20and%20was%20exploring%20ways%20in%20which%20I%20could%20contribute%20to%20the%20community%20directly.%20I%20came%20to%20know%20about%20the%20UPSC%20exam%20from%20my%20college%20friends.%20When%20I%20searched%20more%2C%20I%20came%20to%20know%20this%20work%20can%20not%20only%20help%20me%20engage%20with%20the%20community%20directly%20but%20also%20help%20me%20grow%20personally%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20delved%20into%20the%20world%20of%20competitive%20exams%20after%20his%20graduation%20in%202018%2C%20Akash%20encountered%20further%20hurdles%3B%20the%20first%20of%20which%20was%20his%20Gujarati-medium%20education.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20quality%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360088%2Fupsc-cse-hindi-medium-aspirants-ifs-officer-vikas-singh-meena-shares-tips-study-material-current-affairs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%20material%3C%2Fa%3E%20available%20in%20my%20native%20language.%20I%20sought%20out%20notes%20from%20toppers%20but%20I%20faced%20difficulties%20in%20comprehending%20the%20English-language%20content.%20For%20most%20of%20the%20words%2C%20I%20would%20have%20to%20refer%20to%20dictionaries%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20initial%20struggles%2C%20he%20qualified%20the%20prelims%20in%202019%20but%20failed%20the%20Mains%20exam.%20He%20appeared%20for%20his%20second%20attempt%20in%202022.%20Although%20he%20cleared%20the%20prelims%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353815%2Fias-officer-ashish-kumar-singhal-jaipur-cleared-upsc-cse-after-four-failures-topper%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMains%20exams%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20failed%20at%20the%20interview%20stage.%20However%2C%20he%20achieved%20this%20feat%20while%20working%20as%20a%20tax%20inspector%20in%20Jamnagar%20as%20he%20wanted%20to%20be%20financially%20independent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20his%20experience%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20interview%20round%2C%20I%20opted%20for%20English%20as%20my%20medium%20of%20communication.%20I%20thought%20I%20would%20be%20able%20to%20manage%20but%20I%20fumbled%20in%20my%20interview.%20This%20lowered%20my%20confidence%20level%20and%20I%20failed%20at%20expressing%20myself%20in%20the%20personality%20stage.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20I%20could%20not%20clear%20the%20exam%20in%202022.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Akash%20remained%20undeterred%20and%20cleared%20the%202023%20examination.%20With%20his%20triumphant%20preparation%20journey%2C%20he%20emphasises%20the%20need%20for%20consistency%2C%20self-evaluation%20through%20test%20series%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F205808%2Fias-hero-upsc-topper-tips-general-studies-mains-answer-writing-essay%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewriting%20answers%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20the%20importance%20of%20utilising%20limited%20resources%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20tips%20for%20aspirants%2C%20he%20advises%2C%20%E2%80%9CGet%20a%20good%20understanding%20of%20the%20syllabus%2C%20and%20solve%20previous%20years%E2%80%9