%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalkfit%20aims%20to%20be%20a%20preventive%20strategy%20for%20this%20massive%20problem.%20The%20duo%20worked%20with%20physiotherapists%20to%20understand%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296115%2Fteenagers-startup-finance4teens-educate-kids-globally-on-banking-financial-literacy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiomechanics%20of%20falls%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Meghavi%20Desai%20Bhuptani%2C%20one%20of%20the%20physiotherapists%20who%20helped%20the%20students%2C%20says%20that%20the%20device%20can%20be%20very%20helpful%20for%20people%20who%20lack%20stability.%20%E2%80%9COsteoarthritis%2C%20caused%20due%20to%20wear%20and%20tear%20of%20your%20joints%20sets%20in%20after%20an%20age%20for%20almost%20everyone.%20We%20tend%20to%20recommend%20assistive%20devices%20for%20many%20such%20people%20post%2070%20or%20so%20to%20deal%20with%20imbalance.%20The%20mapping%20done%20by%20Walkfit%20can%20help%20users%20improve%20their%20gait%20and%20prevent%20falls.%20It%20will%20also%20be%20very%20useful%20for%20people%20who%20have%20suffered%20a%20stroke%20or%20have%20Parkinson%E2%80%99s%20disease%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPreventing%20falls%20through%20tech%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWalkfit%20comes%20with%20six%20pressure%20sensors%2C%20which%20are%20strategically%20placed%20on%20the%20stick%2C%20with%20two%20on%20the%20grip%20and%20four%20on%20the%20base.%20The%20system%20analyses%20the%20pressure%20exerted%20on%20the%20stick%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20determine%20the%20user%E2%80%99s%20dependency%20on%20it.%20It%20can%20help%20diagnose%20potential%20health%20issues%20based%20on%20the%20pressure%20patterns%20detected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FnlXbceBCGtY%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26rel%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D1%26controls%3D1%26color%3Dred%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20analysing%20pressure%20values%2C%20we%20assess%20how%20dependent%20the%20user%20is%20on%20the%20stick.%20A%20high%20level%20of%20dependence%20indicates%20a%20greater%20risk%20of%20falling.%20We%20measure%20how%20much%20of%20the%20user%E2%80%99s%20weight%20is%20being%20supported%20by%20the%20stick%3B%20based%20on%20that%2C%20we%20predict%20the%20likelihood%20of%20a%20fall%20and%20help%20diagnose%20potential%20problems%20or%20underlying%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Rahi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20circuit%2C%20equipped%20with%20Bluetooth%20modules%2C%20transmits%20data%20to%20a%20laptop%2C%20generating%20real-time%20heat%20maps.%20These%20heat%20maps%20actually%20show%20which%20pressure%20points%20on%20the%20stick%20are%20bearing%20the%20most%20weight%2C%20giving%20an%20insight%20into%20what%20the%20problem%20could%20be%2C%20or%20what%20the%20chances%20of%20fall%20can%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20heat%20maps%20visually%20represent%20pressure%20points%2C%20with%20blue%20indicating%20low%20pressure%20and%20red%20indicating%20high%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20an%20example%2C%20the%20students%20say%20that%20if%20the%20map%20shows%20high%20pressure%20on%20the%20left%20side%2C%20there%20is%20a%20probability%20that%20the%20user%20has%20a%20problem%20with%20the%20right%20knee%20or%20ankle.%20%E2%80%9CGenerally%2C%20when%20you%20have%20a%20problem%2C%20you%20tend%20to%20put%20less%20weight%20on%20that%20area%2C%20so%20that%20it%20pains%20less.%20You%20tilt%20more%20towards%20the%20opposite%20side%2C%20and%20hence%20the%20left%20side%2C%20which%20shows%20the%20highest%20pressure%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20explain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students%20plan%20to%20develop%20a%20mobile%20app%20in%20the%20future%20to%20make%20this%20data%20more%20accessible%20to%20users.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20elders%20have%20lower%20body%20issues%20like%20osteoarthritis%2C%20osteoporosis%2C%20buckling%20knees%2C%20and%20hip%20fractures.%20Our%20device%20can%20predict%20falls%20in%20both%20standing%20and%20sitting%20positions.%20It%20detects%20stability%20in%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20gait%20and%20changes%20in%20balance%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Hriday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20641px)%20100vw%2C%20641px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-21-at-18.55.14-1724247056.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20circuit%20attaches%20to%20any%20walking%20stick%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22641%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-21-at-18.55.14-1724247056.jpeg%20641w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-21-at-18.55.14-1724247056-267x300.jpeg%20267w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-21-at-18.55.14-1724247056-500x562.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-21-at-18.55.14-1724247056-150x168.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-362430%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20circuit%20attaches%20to%20any%20walking%20stick%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20v