ndia.com%2F317569%2Fharyana-startup-senior-citizen-travel-vacation-plan-seniorworld-redefine-ageing%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eray%20of%20hope%20for%20many%20senior%20citizens%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20were%20abandoned%20by%20their%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Chandrakant%20Navinbhai%20Gajjar.%20Long%20hours%20spent%20weaving%20left%20Chandrakant%20blind.%20When%20he%20turned%20to%20his%20family%20for%20support%2C%20he%20did%20not%20find%20it.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20started%20ignoring%20me%2C%20causing%20frustration%20and%20social%20isolation.%20It%20became%20unbearable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20In%202017%2C%20Chandrakant%E2%80%99s%20brother%20introduced%20him%20to%20Shri%20Navchetan%20Andhjan%20Mandal%20where%20he%20says%20he%20found%20dignity%20at%20long%20last.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20provided%20me%20with%20good%20care%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-2_11zon-1723031266.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Medicines%2C%20food%2C%20clothing%20and%20a%20comfortable%20atmosphere%20are%20provided%20to%20the%20senior%20citizens%20at%20Shri%20Navchetan%20Andhjan%20Mandal%2C%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-2_11zon-1723031266.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-2_11zon-1723031266-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-2_11zon-1723031266-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-2_11zon-1723031266-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fold-age-home-2_11zon-1723031266-15