med%2C%20and%20she%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20at%20a%20pool%20in%20Nashik%2C%20both%20before%20and%20after%20school.%20Her%20dedication%20led%20her%20to%20become%20a%20champion%20swimmer%20at%20the%20school%20and%20district%20levels.%20However%2C%20after%20Class%209%2C%20swimming%20took%20a%20backseat%20as%20her%20studies%20became%20the%20priority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20next%2018%20years%2C%20education%2C%20business%2C%20marriage%2C%20and%20raising%20kids%20took%20precedence%2C%20and%20her%20sport%20faded%20into%20the%20background.%20As%20a%20young%20mother%2C%20she%20juggled%20these%20roles%20while%20longing%20for%20the%20determined%20young%20girl%20who%20once%20embraced%20every%20challenge.%20The%20demands%20of%20everyday%20life%20%E2%80%94%20managing%20a%20resort%20in%20Nashik%2C%20and%20being%20a%20mother%2C%20wife%2C%20and%20daughter%20%E2%80%94%20began%20to%20take%20their%20toll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHad%20she%20lost%20herself%2C%20along%20with%20the%20fearless%20young%20girl%20who%20was%20up%20for%20any%20challenge%2C%20she%20wondered%3F%20This%20search%20for%20self-love%20led%20her%20back%20to%20her%20first%20love%3A%20water.%20One%20might%20think%20she%20would%20simply%20return%20to%20swimming%2C%20but%20Tanvi%20had%20loftier%20dreams.%20Instead%20of%20just%20diving%20back%20into%20the%20pool%2C%20she%20set%20herself%20a%20Herculean%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202022%2C%20over%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%2C%20she%20confided%20in%20her%20husband%20about%20her%20wish%20to%20fulfil%20one%20of%20her%20childhood%20dreams%20%E2%80%94%20to%20swim%20the%20English%20Channel%2C%20a%20daunting%20long-distance%20challenge%20spanning%20over%2033%20km%20from%20England%20to%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20dream%20had%20taken%20root%20when%20she%20was%20just%20a%20child%2C%20inspired%20by%20an%20article%20she%20read%20about%20a%20swimmer%20who%20had%20accomplished%20this%20incredible%20feat.%20Even%20before%20setting%20foot%20in%20a%20pool%2C%20the%2033-year-old%20took%20a%20bold%20step%20and%20registered%20herself%20for%20the%20swim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-deore-1723814698.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tanvi%20stepped%20into%20a%20pool%20after%2018%20years%20in%202022.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-deore-1723814698.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-deore-1723814698-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-deore-1723814698-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-deore-1723814698-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-deore-1723814698-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361692%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETanvi%20stepped%20into%20a%20pool%20after%2018%20years%20in%202022.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20two%20years%2C%20she%20left%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20making%20this%20dream%20a%20reality.%20In%20June%202024%2C%20she%20successfully%20swam%20the%20unforgiving%20waters%20from%20Dover%2C%20UK%2C%20to%20France%20in%2017%20hours%20and%2042%20minutes.%20Along%20the%20way%2C%20she%20braved%20jellyfish%20stings%2C%20challenging%20tides%2C%20and%20the%20notorious%20%E2%80%98swimmer%E2%80%99s%20grave%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20circuit%20that%20trapped%20her%20in%20the%20same%20spot%20for%20over%20three%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20she%20achieved%20this%20ambitious%20goal%2C%20proving%20that%20with%20a%20strong%20will%20and%20determination%2C%20even%20the%20most%20daunting%20obstacles%20can%20be%20overcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20mother%E2%80%99s%20search%20for%20her%20confidence%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanvi%20vividly%20remembers%20the%20day%20she%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332716%2Fjanaki-amma-swimming-lessons-for-women-kids-reduce-drowning-deaths-in-kerala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereturned%20to%20the%20pool%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%202022%2C%20as%20if%20it%20were%20yesterday.%20Swimming%20after%2018%20years%20was%20one%20of%20her%20happiest%20moments%2C%20she%20recalls.%20It%20was%20the%20day%20she%20felt%20whole%20again%2C%20having%20rediscovered%20the%20missing%20piece%20of%20her%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20muscle%20memory%20kicked%20in%20and%20as%20I%20went%20underwater%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20this%20was%20what%20I%20wanted.%20This%20was%20my%20happy%20place.%20I%20cried%20that%20day%20as%20it%20gave%20me%20so%20much%20joy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tanvi%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETanvi%20began%20her%20training%20for%20the%20English%20Channel%20swim%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20coach%20Srikaanth%20Viswanathan%2C%20an%20accomplished%20open-water%20swimmer%20who%20had%20completed%20the%20triple%20crown%20of%20open-water%20swimming.%20Her%20practice%20sessions%20started%20at%204%20am%2C%20requiring%20her%20to%20wake%20up%20at%203%20am.%20The%20sudden%20shift%20in%20routine%20was%20challenging%2C%20especially%20with%20three-year-old%20twins.%20It%20was%20a%20rollercoaster%20ride%2C%20she%20admits%2C%20involving%20a%20complete%20overhaul%20of%20her%20lifestyle%20and%20schedule.%20Her%20children%20were%20too%20young%20to%20grasp%20the%20magnitude%20of%20what%20their%20mother%20was%20attempting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201071px)%20100vw%2C%201071px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%