astic%20waste.%20This%20board%20was%20a%20prototype%20and%20could%20be%20used%20for%20multiple%20applications.%20This%20project%20was%20significant%20as%20it%20allowed%20us%20to%20demonstrate%20the%20practical%20application%20of%20our%20recycling%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20worked%20on%20creating%20eco-friendly%20gifting%20items%2C%20such%20as%20planters%20and%20coasters%2C%20which%20helped%20them%20reach%20a%20wider%20audience%20and%20spread%20awareness%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20recycling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20after%20much%20experimentation%2C%20we%20found%20that%20products%20that%20can%20be%20used%20in%20public%20spaces%20like%20benches%20and%20dustbins%20are%20suitable%20applications%20as%20they%20create%20awareness%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20about%20addressing%20plastic%20waste%20while%20also%20requiring%20vast%20amounts%20of%20recycled%20plastic.%20To%20make%20a%20bench%2C%20for%20example%2C%20we%20require%20approximately%2050%20kg%20of%20plastic%20waste.%20This%20way%20we%20could%20create%20a%20larger%20impact%20and%20soon%20we%20started%20developing%20such%20products%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSonal-Startup-2-1723642173.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sonal%20was%20selected%20as%20a%20leader%20for%20the%20Women%20Climate%20Collective%202024%2C%20a%20platform%20for%20supporting%20emerging%20women%20leaders%20to%20lead%20climate%20action.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSonal-Startup-2-1723642173.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSonal-Startup-2-1723642173-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSona