ces%2C%20including%20informal%20waste%20workers%20who%20collect%20materials%20from%20different%20locations.%20They%20also%20collaborate%20with%20NGOs%2C%20housing%20societies%2C%20and%20colleges%20to%20run%20awareness%20campaigns%20and%20collect%20plastic%20through%20source%20segregation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20collecting%20the%20plastic%20waste%2C%20we%20sort%20and%20clean%20it%20thoroughly.%20After%20the%20plastic%20waste%20is%20collected%2C%20it%20is%20meticulously%20sorted%20to%20separate%20different%20types%20of%20plastic.%20This%20sorting%20process%20is%20crucial%20because%20different%20plastics%20have%20different%20properties%20and%20melting%20points%2C%20which%20affect%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20final%20product%20as%20well%20as%20the%20recyclability%20of%20the%20recycled%20products.%20Hence%20we%20do%20not%20mix%20different%20plastic%20types%20ensuring%20it%20is%20again%20recyclable%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Sonal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%E2%80%99s%20their%20%E2%80%98value-based%20recycling%20technology%E2%80%99%20that%20makes%20%3Cem%3Eeconscious%20%3C%2Fem%3Eunique%20and%20impactful%2C%20argues%20Sonal.%20Unlike%20traditional%20recycling%20methods%2C%20which%20often%20produce%20low-quality%20items%2C%20she%20claims%20their%20approach%20ensures%20that%20the%20recycled%20plastic%20products%20they%20create%20are%20high-quality%20and%20practical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTraditional%20recycling%20often%20involves%20turning%20plastic%20into%20small%20pellets%2C%20which%20consumes%20a%20lot%20of%20energy.%20Instead%2C%20we%20skip%20the%20pellet-making%20process%20and%20use%20plastic%20flakes.%20This%20choice%20not%20only%20saves%20energy%20but%20also%20reduces%20our%20environmental%20impact%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Sonal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20then%20turn%20these%20plastic%20flakes%20into%20eco-boards.%20This%20is%20where%20our%20value-based%20recycling%20plays%20a%20key%20role.%20The%20eco-boards%20are%20durable%20and%20versatile%2C%20serving%20as%20raw%20materials%20for%20various%20high-quality%20products%20and%20applications.%20This%20process%20is%20energy-efficient%20and%20helps%20maintain%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20plastic%2C%20allowing%20us%20to%20create%20long-lasting%20and%20valuable%20items%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSonal-Startup-1-1723642660.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sonal%20is%20seen%20here%20explaining%20the%20product%20and%20process.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSonal-Startup-1-1723642660.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSonal-Startup-1-1723642660-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSonal-Startup-1-1723642660-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSonal-Startup-1-1723642660-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSonal-Startup-1-1723642660-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361521%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESonal%20is%20seen%20here%20explaining%20the%20product%20and%20process.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20are%20these%20eco-boards%20more%20specifically%3F%20Eco-boards%20are%20produced%20using%20compression%20moulding%20technology%2C%20where%20small%20flakes%20of%20specific%20types%20of%20plastic%20waste%20are%20compressed%20to%20make%20boards%20of%20various%20thicknesses%20ranging%20from%208%20mm%20up%20to%2018%20mm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20process%20is%20not%20only%20environmentally%20friendly%20but%20also%20allows%20u